Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.78,0:00:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.99,0:00:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是诺亚先生的信
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.62,0:00:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的吗？
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.49,0:00:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 信就放在柜台上
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.88,0:00:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和多米姐姐在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}说着不要松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:40.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}或者不要溶解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:45.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}从身处的世界向抵抗的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:49.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}在迎面而来的风中绽放 Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:54.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}那瞳孔声音震颤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.05,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}What's the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:59.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}呼喊的日子 Blurry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:04.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}呼喊的日子 Blurry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:09.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(200,200)}向希望侧耳倾听
